data.description: OWNER MUST GO! PRICE REDUCED! Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this 4 bed, 2 bath home offers an abundance of space and amenities, situated on a sprawling 1-acre lot with 50 shares of Grandview Ditch. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, boasting a generous size and original hardwood floors that exude timeless charm. It's the perfect sanctuary for rest and relaxation after a long day. The large living room boosts natural light for that airy feeling with peek-a-boo views of the surrounding fields and hills. The full basement is partial finished but currently is complimented with 2 bedrooms, 2 living spaces, a workout room, and walk in pantry.  The 1 acre lot is fenced and is accompanied by a 2 car detached garage, 30x40 loafing shed, garden area and more. Plenty of room to park any recreational vehicles and more. Enjoy the tranquility of rural living while still being conveniently close to schools, shopping, and amenities.
